<h2 id="my-favourite-articles">My Favourite Articles</h2>

<ul>
  <li><a href="https://www.thecrimson.com/article/2017/5/25/desai-commencement-ed/">Optionality</a> - on optimizing for optionality vs committing</li>
  <li><a href="https://dcgross.com/10X/">10X: Metrics for Early Stage Startups</a> - mini playbook on getting products from 0 to 1</li>
  <li><a href="https://www.trevormckendrick.com/essays/the-perfect-decision-fallacy">The Perfect Decision Fallacy</a> - on making big decisions or reaching big goals (tldr: think of it instead as a series of small decisions along the way and that there are very many ways to get there)</li>
</ul>

